# credentials.json is intentionally TRACKED, not ignored — it's an installed-app OAuth
# client config (mit-workspace-mcp-server). Google treats installed-app client secrets as
# non-confidential; the real secret is the refresh token (token.json, ignored below).
# Distributed publicly by design — also vendored in spm1001/batterie. Confirmed posture
# 2026-06-28 (mise-dumebo). Do NOT re-add an ignore line or `git rm` it. See CLAUDE.md OAuth.

